OL,5, More than half of licensed taxi drivers
OL,6, have not returned to the trade since   
OL,7, the pandemic, the organisation         
OL,8, representing the industry has said.    
OL,10,FThe Licensed Private Car Hire          
OL,11,FAssociation (LPCHA) estimates the      
OL,12,Findustry is short of 160,000 of the    
OL,13,Fpreviously 300,000-strong workforce.   
OL,15,FMany drivers left the industry during  
OL,16,Flockdowns as demand plummeted.         
OL,18,FThe shortage has prompted concerns over
OL,19,Fthe safety of women, students and night
OL,20,Ftime workers struggling to get home.   
